help:python colors;help:scripting colors
To see the basics about types see :help set types.
To see the basics about scripting see :help set python.

gf.addColorAlias(alias, color)
  Creates named color or named color with opacity
  according to the given color.
gf.resetColorAliases()
  Removes all named colors.

gf.normalizeColor(color)
gf.normalizeColorAlpha(color)
  Returns the color in the normalized form:
    #RRGGBB, or #AARRGGBB resp.
    (all letters A-F are capital)
  Trying to return a color with opacity without it
  is treated as exception.
